1. Place this directory in source/user/ifx/ of your platform source code.
2. You can modify your configuration files so as to include this directory for your build.
3. Once building is done, module ip_turbonat.o gets created in /lib/modules in root file system.
4. You have to modify your init scripts so as to load the module, at the time of your bootup.
5. For this feature to work, Turbonat feature has to be enabled in the kernel. Configuring this option in the kernel,
is necessary, but not sufficient. The feature works, only when this module is loaded.
6. This feature might have some side effects. Please refer LXDB 1.1 User manual for complete details.

